title: EMC Isilon: Disk Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/storagehw/emc
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 Checks the Status of Disks in EMC Isilon Storage Systems.

 Returns {OK} if the disk is HEALTHY and {CRIT} on every other status.

item:
 The ID of the disk bay.

discovery:
 One service is created for each disk in an EMC Isilon Storage.
